Keybindings

ctl+v : page down
alt+v : page up
f5 : complete
ctl+l : center line

MOVE
ctl+b : Character backward
ctl+f : Character forward
alt+b : Word backward
alt+f : Word forward
ctl+p : Line previous
ctl+n : Line next
ctl+a : Line backward
ctl+e : Line forward
alt+a : Sentence backward
alt+e : Sentence forward
alt+{ : Paragraph backward
alt+} : Paragraph forward
alt+< : beginning of file
alt+> : end of file

SELECT (MOVE)
sft+ctl+b : Character backward
sft+ctl+f : Character forward
sft+alt+b : Word backward
sft+alt+f : Word forward
sft+ctl+p : Line previous
sft+ctl+n : Line next
sft+ctl+a : Line backward
sft+ctl+e : Line forward
sft+alt+a : Sentence backward
sft+alt+e : Sentence forward
sft+cmd+alt+{ : Paragraph backward
sft+cmd+alt+} : Paragraph forward

SELECT CURRENT
alt+w : Word
cmd+l : Line
alt+cmd+l : Sentence
cmd+alt+l + Paragraph

DELETE (MOVE)
ctl+d : delete character forward
alt+d : delete one word forward
Del : delte character backward
FwD : delete character forward
alt+Del : delete word backward
alt+FwD : delete one word forward
cmd+Del : Line backward
cmd+FwD : Line forward

SEARCHING
C-s : search
C-r : search backwards (if available)
ctl+alt+s : regex search forward
ctl+alt+r : regex saerch backward
